# AI Resume Analyzer

A backend application built with FastAPI and PostgreSQL that allows users to:

* Register and log in securely
* Authenticate using JWT tokens
* Upload resumes
* Analyze resumes for technical skills
* Store analysis results
* View resume and analysis history

## Tech Stack

* Python
* FastAPI
* PostgreSQL
* SQLAlchemy
* JWT Authentication
* Passlib (bcrypt)

## Features

* User Registration
* User Login
* Protected Routes
* Resume Upload
* Resume Analysis
* Analysis History

## Run Locally

pip install -r requirements.txt

uvicorn main:app --reload

## API Endpoints

POST /users

POST /login

POST /upload-resume

POST /analyze-resume/{resume_id}

GET /my-resumes

GET /my-analyses
